## Cohesion Audit: Oliver-Tree.md

### Central Thesis
Oliver Tree was an Enneagram Type 4 who deliberately turned himself into an absurd meme so the sincere artist underneath could smuggle real feeling past everyone — and his death being read as a hoax is the final proof of how completely he built that disguise.

